<dt>Overviews</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070404004937/http://www.aegistrust.org/" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070404004937/http://www.aegistrust.org/" rel="nofollow">"Aegis Trust (genocide prevention trust)"</a>. Archived from <a href="http://www.aegistrust.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.aegistrust.org/" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2007-04-04<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070404004937/http://www.aegistrust.org/" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070404004937/http://www.aegistrust.org/" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20070404004937/http://www.aegistrust.org/</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Aegis+Trust+%28genocide+prevention+trust%29&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070404004937%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.aegistrust.org%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Genocide"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> An independent international organisation dedicated to eliminating genocide</li>
<li><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/1701562.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/1701562.stm" rel="nofollow">BBC on defining genocide</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ushmm.org/conscience/" class="external text" title="http://www.ushmm.org/conscience/" rel="nofollow">Committee on Conscience of the United States Holocaust Memorial Museum</a>; Responding to Threats of Genocide</li>
<li><a href="http://www.law-ref.org/GENOCIDE/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.law-ref.org/GENOCIDE/index.html" rel="nofollow">Convention on the Prevention and Punishment of the Crime of Genocide at Law-Ref.org</a> - fully indexed and crosslinked with other documents</li>
<li><a href="http://www.warcrimes.info/" class="external text" title="http://www.warcrimes.info/" rel="nofollow">Documents and Resources on War, War Crimes and Genocide</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.facinghistory.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.facinghistory.org/" rel="nofollow">Facing History and Ourselves</a></li>
